survey_response.review_text: I got my painless root canal treatment done in July this year from Dr.Gagan Khanna, and got two porcelain crowns also installed. The color of the crowns matches the color of my teeth. It feels comfortable in mouth. These crowns comes under 5 year warranty and can last longer with good maintenance, so I am ok with the cost. My 2 canine teeth are not in the right place and the front teeth are slightly crooked. So I will definitely visit again for the treatment (without braces and aligners) to improve my smile and health of my mouth. The doctor is friendly and will give you many solutions to a problem and then you can choose the best option for you.

survey_response.review_text: We went for the first time to meet Dr. Gagan for a dental complication. He was very warmly welcoming, gave us ample time to  make us underatand the problem and various alternative treatments possible, with their respective pros and cons. Apart from 'theory', he has vast experience of 'practical' aspects of how tooth will behave with a given issue over time. Finally he gave a  very simplified solution. I really really liked his down-to-earth and charming demeanor which made us very comfortable to ask any questions. Further, he didn't suggest us any unnecessary & costly treatments and stressed on preserving natural good health of teeth. Surely, he is a highly recommendable dental expert in Delhi. Thanks Dr. Gagan👍🙏!!!
